# 18aac4eca8ec481386a9c8da8aa5e856
#: ../../gui.rst:141
msgid ""
"**Send to card (B)**: The selected books are transferred to the storage card"
" (B) on the ebook reader."
msgstr "**Enviar a la tarjeta de memoria B**: Los libros seleccionados se copian a la tarjeta de memoria (B) en el dispositivo de lectura."

# 94988611ff4f4f3d8b098f0ac9b770ea
#: ../../gui.rst:142
